Package: nsjail
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, libkafel1, libprotobuf32t64, libnl-route-3-200
Description: process isolation tool for Linux
 NsJail is a process isolation tool for Linux. It utilizes Linux namespace
 subsystem, resource limits, and the seccomp-bpf syscall filters of the Linux
 kernel.
